    "explanation": "{{nOut}} bar(s) fall outside the limits ({{outLow}} below the LSL, {{outHigh}} above the USL). Height is a red herring — a tall in-spec bar is fine, a short out-of-spec bar is still a defect; only the position relative to each limit decides it."
